Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Removes the AppInit_DLLs shim (run this if you no longer need the shim
; or want to go back to the fls30_loader.exe injection method).

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Windows]
"AppInit_DLLs"=""
"LoadAppInit_DLLs"=dword:00000000
